    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔气入侵，魔道肆虐。经营镇魔塔，庇护四方百姓</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模拟经营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在魔道入侵前，获取足够多的资源，及时提升战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/e2c0a4087125353abf824331d001adee.poster.avif?t=1738678065\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/e2c0a4087125353abf824331d001adee.webm?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/e2c0a4087125353abf824331d001adee.mp4?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实现香客祈福，获得百姓供奉的铜钱和材料。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/8f2888b0a8736215694d82d0c7b10ca1.poster.avif?t=1738678065\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/8f2888b0a8736215694d82d0c7b10ca1.webm?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/8f2888b0a8736215694d82d0c7b10ca1.mp4?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 提升阵法卷轴，强化战斗属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔道入侵</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/354d3bf7684f899645c31bc7e6235bf8.poster.avif?t=17386