video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/ff796c1fce78474cea30bb7d2bbb3650.poster.avif?t=1738678065\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/ff796c1fce78474cea30bb7d2bbb3650.webm?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331170/extras/ff796c1fce78474cea30bb7d2bbb3650.mp4?t=1738678065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >部署印记</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署印记规划路线，规避伤害。运筹帷幄，于随机中掌乾坤。</p>",
